        <item>
            <title>【评测】NETGEAR Nighthawk MK92   三频 WiFi 6E Mesh + 提升隔墙上网速度</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/15/netgear-nighthawk-mk92-2/wireless-home/routers/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=netgear-nighthawk-mk92-2</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/15/netgear-nighthawk-mk92-2/wireless-home/routers/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 10:45:54 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[家居无线]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[路由器]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[NETGEAR]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[NETGEAR Nighthawk MK92]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Wi-Fi 6E]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1228536</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>随著科技发展，即使安坐家中，相信大家都会手执电话、手提电脑、游戏机、平板等多部装置连接网络，如用家需要欣赏 4K HDR 影片、Hi-Res 音乐等，对频宽要求只会有增无减，对网络连接的需求亦相应提高。若你需要更快更稳定的网络连接设备，就要考虑购置 Wi-Fi 6E Mesh Wi-Fi 装置。今次我们会实测 NETGEAR 近日推出的 Nighthawk 系列最新产品：MK92 Mesh Wi-Fi 6 路由器，看看它如何解决上网死角问题。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1228776" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc09434-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc09434-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc09434.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>MK72S 是一款高速三频 Wi-Fi 6 Mesh System，其 5GHz 及 6GHz Wi-Fi 频道可支援 160MHz 频道，令无线传输可媲美传统有线传输，而且表现比同级数其他产品更为优秀及穏定。全新四核心 1.7 GHz 的处理器比以往的型号支援更多装置同时上网，即使是多装置使用的重度网络使用者都十分适合。</p><h2>顶部浮雕设计，盒状机身融入家居</h2><p>今次评测的 NETGEAR Nighthawk MK92 外观设计简约，机顶设计是简单大方的网格状正方立体浮雕，简约之余亦不失细致。</p><p>包装内有一个主路由器和一个衞星子机。Nighhawk MK92 机身四正，放在家中不会突兀。而今次外壳使用的材料是高反光钢琴面塑胶，质感满满，惟一要批评的是捉摸后容易留下指纹。整个机身设计四正，占地不多，适合在家居任何位置安装。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1228777" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc09423-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc09423-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc09423.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1228778" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc09429-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc09429-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc09429.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲机顶立方体浮雕设计感觉时尚</p><h2>机身接口多，按需求连接</h2><p>Nighthawk MK92 的路由器 MK92 主机提供 1 个 2.5Gig 网际网路埠及 3 个以太网埠，分机亦提供 2 个以太网埠，让用家可以连接游戏机、电脑、IoT 设备等装置。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1228781" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc09428-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc09428-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc09428.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲路由器主机提供 2.5Gig 网际网路埠及 3 个以太网埠</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1228780" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc09426-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc09426-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc09426.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲路由器主机（上）；衞星分机（下）提供 2 个以太网埠</p><p>&nbsp;<br /><br /><b>相关文章:</b></p><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/05/netgear-nighthawk-mk92/wireless-home/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">NETGEAR 全新 WiFi 6E Mesh 系统   Nighthawk MK92 三频 WiFi 适合高达 5,000 呎环境</a></li><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/05/netgear-april-sale/wireless-home/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">NETGEAR 四月优惠推介  2.5G WAN、WiFi 6E、WiFi 7 路由器出机优惠</a></li><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/25/netgear-wifi-6e-product-sale-2024-spring/wireless-home/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">NETGEAR 全线 WiFi 6E 产品特价，初春优惠推介</a></li></blockquote><p></p><h2>安装方便，一个 App 即可完成设定</h2><p>用家只需要插上电源线，其后连接 LAN 线和主机，就能够完成主路由器最初硬件设置。而主机初始设定亦简易明了。为顾及新手，Netgear 推出了 Nighthawk 专用应用程式，替主路由器和衞星子机连接电源并开机后，下载 NETGEAR Nighthawk 手机 App ，申请 Netgear 帐户后，只要扫描路由器的 QR Code，其后的手续就可交由应用程式自动设置。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1228794" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo1712827987-268x580.jpeg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo1712827987-268x580.jpeg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo1712827987.jpeg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲下载「NETGEAR Nighthawk」应用程式</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1179926" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/netgear1-268x580.png" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/netgear1-268x580.png 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/netgear1-416x900.png 416w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/netgear1.png 591w" alt="" width="268" height="580" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲注册「NETGEAR」帐户</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1179926" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/netgear1-268x580.png" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/netgear1-268x580.png 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/netgear1-416x900.png 416w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/netgear1.png 591w" alt="" width="268" height="580" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲注册「NETGEAR」帐户</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1228795" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo17128279871-268x580.jpeg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo17128279871-268x580.jpeg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo17128279871.jpeg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲选择你的产品，小编手上的是 Nighthawk Mesh 系统</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1228796" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo17128279872-268x580.jpeg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo17128279872-268x580.jpeg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo17128279872.jpeg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲扫描路由器底部的 QR Code</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1228797" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo1712827991-268x580.jpeg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo1712827991-268x580.jpeg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo1712827991.jpeg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Netgear Nighthawk 应用程式会自动替你完成剩下的步骤</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1228798" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo17128279911-268x580.jpeg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo17128279911-268x580.jpeg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo17128279911.jpeg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲此时需要按「加入」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1228799" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo17128279912-268x580.jpeg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo17128279912-268x580.jpeg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo17128279912.jpeg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1228800" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo17128279913-268x580.jpeg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo17128279913-268x580.jpeg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo17128279913.jpeg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Nighthawk 应用程式会自动替你扫描衞星子机</p><p style="text-align: left;">等手机连接到路由器和衞星子机便可直接上网了。用户事后如果想调整任何设定，亦可利用 Nighthawk 手机 App 遥距管理。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1228801" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo1712828807-268x580.jpeg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo1712828807-268x580.jpeg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo1712828807.jpeg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲看见这个页面就代表已经完成扫描所有衞星子机</p><h2>网速测试</h2><p>MK90 是三频 Mesh Wi-Fi 6E 装置，能够连接更多装置，覆盖范围和网络表现更佳。我们在办公室进行实际测试，尝试在复杂环境下如何解决无线网络讯号问题。使用 Netgear Nighthawk 应用程式内置的网络测速功能可得出下载 2314.30 Mbps、上传 965.72 Mbps 和 9ms 延迟的测试结果。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229423" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/787e0e11b6e44c83a52a-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/787e0e11b6e44c83a52a-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/787e0e11b6e44c83a52a.jpg 415w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Netgear Nighthawk 应用程式内置的网络测速功能</p><p>首先我们在路由器 2 米范围内，Samsung S24 Ultra 手机装上「Speedtest」网络测速软件测得下载 1,901 Mbps，上载 1,207 Mbps，延迟 5 ms。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229417" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/screenshot_20240415_-293x580.jpg" alt="" width="293" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/screenshot_20240415_-293x580.jpg 293w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/screenshot_20240415_-scaled.jpg 455w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 293px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲离路由器 2 米（没有墙壁阻隔）</p><p>小编在没有墙壁阻隔的情况下，Samsung S24 Ultra 手机距离路由器约 5 米再使用测速软件，测得下载 1,574 Mbps，上载 1,158 Mbps，延迟仍能够保持在 5 ms。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229419" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/screenshot_20240415_-2-293x580.jpg" alt="" width="293" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/screenshot_20240415_-2-293x580.jpg 293w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/screenshot_20240415_-2-scaled.jpg 455w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 293px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲离路由器 5 米的测试结果（没有墙壁阻隔）</p><p>小编这次在隔住一面墙，Samsung S24 Ultra 手机远离路由器 10 米的情况下使用测速软件，下载录得 1,002 Mbps，上载 770 Mbps，延迟只稍为提升至 9 ms，即使隔住一面墙，表现仍然令人满意。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229418" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/screenshot_20240415_-1-293x580.jpg" alt="" width="293" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/screenshot_20240415_-1-293x580.jpg 293w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/screenshot_20240415_-1-scaled.jpg 454w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 293px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲离路由器 10 米的测试结果（中间有一面墙）</p><h2>总结：安装无困难 覆盖范围广</h2><p>Nighthawk MK92 安装非常简单便捷，即使是电脑新手亦能轻松自行安装。实际试用时，可见衞星子机能改善隔墙上网体验，最重要的是新增衞星子机亦非常轻松，全程可以用 App 直接自动设置。<br /><b>相关文章:</b></p><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/05/netgear-nighthawk-mk92/wireless-home/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">NETGEAR 全新 WiFi 6E Mesh 系统   Nighthawk MK92 三频 WiFi 适合高达 5,000 呎环境</a></li><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/05/netgear-april-sale/wireless-home/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">NETGEAR 四月优惠推介  2.5G WAN、WiFi 6E、WiFi 7 路由器出机优惠</a></li><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/25/netgear-wifi-6e-product-sale-2024-spring/wireless-home/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">NETGEAR 全线 WiFi 6E 产品特价，初春优惠推介</a></li></blockquote><p></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/15/netgear-nighthawk-mk92-2/wireless-home/routers/">【评测】NETGEAR Nighthawk MK92   三频 WiFi 6E Mesh + 提升隔墙上网速度</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
